description: When things start to heat up, there's nothing like delicious gelato and sorbet to help you Tropiccool down! Tropiccool's fantastic double-decker bus is here to bring you the frozen treats that are oh so sweet in the Florida heat. All-natural flavors, recipes passed down from the family, and a dedication to quality are what set these frozen treats apart, so look for a Tropiccool good time today!
name: Tropicool
